  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/3549d7b9462414d405ef6c36b3aa99be.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=980 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Rage Against the Machine</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Roguelite. Horde Survival. Squad-Builder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world threatened by M.E.G.A. Corp.’s private robot army, the last bastion of hope for mankind is a bunch of armed lunatics who signed up for a mercenary job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who's better to lead them than a disposable clone with an unpredictable set of special traits? Welcome to your new assignment, Commander.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the battle to the enemy and build your underfunded, over-ambitious outfit into an apocalyptic war machine that rids the world of evil billionaire overlords.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With all chances stacked against you, this isn’t about glory. This is about the loot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/89d307f03613920f2cbe5805954662cc.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clone your every Commander with randomly selected traits. Can you lead your squad to victory with a hawk-eyed, sly Infiltrator? Or battle solo as a nocturnal, greedy One-Man Army? How about a brilliant, vampiric Ninja?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each combination of traits yields a unique run with its own set of challenges, mechanics, and surprising synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your favorite weapon and unleash havoc! But first, you need a squad:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/5df728d28fcb9c27393ae14b67bd9da0.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble your mercenary team from a roster of vigorous fighters. Each Merc totes their own arsenal and personal tactics to tackle the robot horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call in your Merc clone reinforcements, pick their optimal specialization tree for your operation, and supercharge their combat effectiveness with hi-tech Gear to build a game-breaking, horde-slaying killer squad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/8d548fbedecc8b6c14d38f5aa36256d6.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct your operations against M.E.G.A. Corp. and its subsidiaries through multiple stages on a variety of procedurally generated maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture objectives to call in reinforcements, fulfill missions, and sack valuable loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strike hard and fast! The clock is ticking - each minute on the battlefield means more, stronger enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/c02973bc83a5b7247d3fbf1351f2be36.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to the extraction point and defend it until your choppa takes you to the next stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight and survive long enough to face the unique, massive bosses and their underlings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware: it's all or nothing! Die, and lose your loot. Survive, and take home your spoils of war to come back even stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/db1dd0dc60693720a5094cc60d25d96e.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your loot to hire new Mercs, purchase new Gear, expand your bunker HQ with permenent upgrades, or research new traits & weapons for your Commander clones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/017df25e673b28c4c2a555b71f95c3c7.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide your Mercs with tactical abilities or focus on fighting actively in the battle – each Commander clone and loadout offers its own individual tactical choice and style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment to find your optimal squad build for any challenge M.E.G.A. Corp. throws at you. No two runs are the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/ea0133a9607a8d0ce2ebfb3d855483be.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control an individual Commander clone generated from over 15,000 combinations of unique Traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your squad into battle and actively aim, shoot, dash and fight alongside your Mercs with dozens of twin-stick weapons and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your squad from a large roster of Mercs with unique loadouts, behavior & specialization trees.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find dozens of powerful Gear items to modify and improve your squad in each operation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct your Operations on distinct, procedural Maps with different stages, mission parameters, difficulty tiers, and unique Bosses, Elites, and enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Story Missions to meet your Mercs, grow your arsenal, and cross the secret plans of the M.E.G.A. Corp. bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your Bunker HQ with Rooms built and upgraded with the loot you’ve scavenged in your operations to unlock more tactical options and permanent bonuses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with your friends in couch co-op to wreak havoc - or join forces via Steam Remote Play Together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full support for all controllers and keyboard + mouse controls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stream the game with a custom Twitch integration and let your audience decide your fate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully compatible and verified on SteamDeck</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Rage Against the Machine</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Roguelite. Horde Survival. Squad-Builder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/2691c236f6d7cfd723a7360a8adc6993.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world threatened by M.E.G.A. Corp.’s private robot army, the last bastion of hope for mankind is a bunch of armed lunatics who signed up for a mercenary job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who's better to lead them than a disposable clone with an unpredictable set of special traits? Welcome to your new assignment, Commander.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the battle to the enemy and build your underfunded, over-ambitious outfit into an apocalyptic war machine that rids the world of evil billionaire overlords.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With all chances stacked against you, this isn’t about glory. This is about the loot!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/89d307f03613920f2cbe5805954662cc.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clone your every Commander with randomly selected traits. Can you lead your squad to victory with a hawk-eyed, sly Infiltrator? Or battle solo as a nocturnal, greedy One-Man Army? How about a brilliant, vampiric Ninja?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each combination of traits yields a unique run with its own set of challenges, mechanics, and surprising synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your favorite weapon and unleash havoc! But first, you need a squad:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/481ec387176633af315ea92123e10efc.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/5df728d28fcb9c27393ae14b67bd9da0.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble your mercenary team from a roster of vigorous fighters. Each Merc totes their own arsenal and personal tactics to tackle the robot horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Call in your Merc clone reinforcements, pick their optimal specialization tree for your operation, and supercharge their combat effectiveness with hi-tech Gear to build a game-breaking, horde-slaying killer squad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/df6de3e5783db96915c1f178fccdf1d1.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/8d548fbedecc8b6c14d38f5aa36256d6.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct your operations against M.E.G.A. Corp. and its subsidiaries through multiple stages on a variety of procedurally generated maps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture objectives to call in reinforcements, fulfill missions, and sack valuable loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strike hard and fast! The clock is ticking - each minute on the battlefield means more, stronger enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/346610e20fa458c5b30dcac574411ea9.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/c02973bc83a5b7247d3fbf1351f2be36.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to the extraction point and defend it until your choppa takes you to the next stage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight and survive long enough to face the unique, massive bosses and their underlings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware: it's all or nothing! Die, and lose your loot. Survive, and take home your spoils of war to come back even stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/a9f1326a47d76cc4fd0bd94003a5e394.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/db1dd0dc60693720a5094cc60d25d96e.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invest your loot to hire new Mercs, purchase new Gear, expand your bunker HQ with permenent upgrades, or research new traits & weapons for your Commander clones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/d8dc5c82a9a476af56902dbe665c70a6.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/017df25e673b28c4c2a555b71f95c3c7.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide your Mercs with tactical abilities or focus on fighting actively in the battle – each Commander clone and loadout offers its own individual tactical choice and style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment to find your optimal squad build for any challenge M.E.G.A. Corp. throws at you. No two runs are the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.poster.avif?t=1774060042\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.webm?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/17361be9d8a2d142b2789b651401a348.mp4?t=1774060042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141520/extras/ea0133a9607a8d0ce2ebfb3d855483be.avif?t=1774060042\" width=616 height=88 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control an individual Commander clone generated from over 15,000 combinations of unique Traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your squad into battle and actively aim, shoot, dash and fight alongside your Mercs with dozens of twin-stick weapons and abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your squad from a large roster of Mercs with unique loadouts, behavior & specialization trees.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find dozens of powerful Gear items to modify and improve your squad in each operation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct your Operations on distinct, procedural Maps with different stages, mission parameters, difficulty tiers, and unique Bosses, Elites, and enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete Story Missions to meet your Mercs, grow your arsenal, and cross the secret plans of the M.E.G.A. Corp. bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your Bunker HQ with Rooms built and upgraded with the loot you’ve scavenged in your operations to unlock more tactical options and permanent bonuses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with your friends in couch co-op to wreak havoc - or join forces via Steam Remote Play Together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full support for all controllers and keyboard + mouse controls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stream the game with a custom Twitch integration and let your audience decide your fate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully compatible and verified on SteamDeck</p></li></ul>",
